            <title>Version 1.0.17</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>Retext 1.0.17</h3>
                <h4>New Features</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Snippet Validation</strong> - Snippets are now validated before saving to prevent issues</li>
                    <li><strong>Infinite Loop Prevention</strong> - The app now detects and prevents snippets that would trigger themselves infinitely</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Improvements</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Added validation for empty titles and content</li>
                    <li>Added warning for titles with spaces</li>
                    <li>Improved test coverage with 41 unit tests</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
